data.title: National Library of Scotland
data.text:
Map Finder- with Marker Pin

Search for all of our online maps by placing a marker on your point of interest. The maps covering the marker location appear in the Results on the right.

This viewer shows all zoom levels (further information).

Select the View 3 zoom levels button (upper right) to view just three zoom levels.

Read the Help to the lower left for further guidance.

Click the cross (top right) to close this window.
